# Numbers to words converter

this project convert integer number into written words

## Installation
Open the project as a existing one and use maven
java 8 was used to complete the assigment
Junit 4 was used to perform testing

## How it works

Please run Main to start to convert numbers
Enter an integer number (negatives and positives are accepted)
Hit enter

Note: When user select letters, decimals or hit enter without setting anything a message will be displayed
"The input is not a valid number"


To run Junits
please go to test folder and look for UnitsConverterTest and run it. Junit will test the project.
Or On IDE console type mvn test (please be sure to have maven installed in your local pc)


